reviewText: if you are into this sort of material, well, you can not get enough.....David is different...have worked with him on  multiple weekend workshops....he is truly knowledgeable, and understands the material....and an accomplished teacher....this is not new age made up junk...the real deal.

These are not bad instruction, I think I gained as much from his YouTube videos though.  I'm not sure of his production costs but his prices seem a bit high and his verbal instructions could be a little better.
